---
import MainLayout from "../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
---

<MainLayout title="Tactonic Technologies">

  <!-- =========================
  HERO
  ========================== -->
<section class="border-b border-gray-200">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-24 lg:py-32">

    <div class="max-w-4xl">

      <p class="text-sm font-semibold tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-gray-500">
        Multi-Axis Force & Pressure Sensing Systems
      </p>

      <h1 class="mt-6 text-5xl md:text-7xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 leading-tight">
        Enabling systems to understand physical interaction through high-resolution force sensing.
      </h1>

      <p class="mt-8 text-xl text-gray-600 leading-8">
        Tactonic Technologies develops solid-state sensing platforms capable of measuring multi-degree-of-freedom force and pressure interactions, enabling precise characterization of contact, shape, and shear dynamics in real time.
      </p>

      <p class="mt-6 text-lg text-gray-600 leading-8">
        These systems provide a foundation for advanced physical intelligence across robotics, industrial automation, and human-machine interaction, where understanding complex contact behavior is essential.
      </p>

      <div class="mt-10 flex gap-4">
        <a href="/technology" class="bg-black text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-lg">
          Explore Technology
        </a>

        <a href="/applications" class="border border-gray-300 px-6 py-3 rounded-lg">
          Applications
        </a>
      </div>

    </div>

  </div>
</section>

  <!-- =========================
  MISSION
  ========================== -->

<section class="py-24">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16">

    <div>
      <h2 class="text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-gray-500">
        Mission
      </h2>

      <p class="mt-4 text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 leading-tight">
        Enabling machines to understand and respond to physical interaction.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-6 text-lg text-gray-600 leading-8">

      <p>
        Physical interaction remains one of the least understood and least
        precisely measured domains in modern engineered systems. Current
        approaches often reduce contact to limited force or pressure signals,
        without capturing the full structure of interaction dynamics.
      </p>

      <p>
        Tactonic Technologies addresses this gap through solid-state multi-axis
        sensing systems that provide high-resolution measurement of force,
        pressure, and shear behavior during real-time contact.
      </p>

      <p>
        Our goal is to enable a new class of systems that can transition from
        simple force detection to meaningful interpretation of physical
        interaction in real-world environments.
      </p>

    </div>

  </div>
</section>

  <!-- =========================
  TECHNOLOGY PREVIEW
  ========================== -->
  <!-- TECHNOLOGY -->
<section class="bg-gray-50 border-y border-gray-200 py-24">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">

    <h2 class="text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-gray-500">
      Technology
    </h2>

    <p class="mt-4 text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 max-w-3xl">
      Solid-state sensing systems for multi-dimensional physical interaction measurement.
    </p>

    <p class="mt-6 text-lg text-gray-600 leading-8 max-w-4xl">
      Tactonic Technologies develops sensing platforms that measure force, pressure, and shear across multiple degrees of freedom, enabling high-resolution capture of contact dynamics in real time.
    </p>

    <div class="mt-16 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">

      <!-- Current Platform -->
      <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-2xl p-8">

        <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900">
          Current Platform — 3 DOF Sensing
        </h3>

        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600 leading-7">
          The current system enables structured measurement of multi-axis force and pressure interactions, providing real-time feedback during physical contact events.
        </p>

        <div class="mt-6 space-y-3 text-gray-700">
          <p>• Multi-axis force and pressure sensing</p>
          <p>• Real-time interaction feedback</p>
          <p>• Contact-aware measurement of physical dynamics</p>
        </div>

      </div>

      <!-- Next Generation -->
      <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-2xl p-8">

        <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900">
          Next Generation — 6 DOF Expansion
        </h3>

        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600 leading-7">
          The next platform expands sensing dimensionality to support richer characterization of interaction dynamics, enabling more complete interpretation of physical contact behavior.
        </p>

        <div class="mt-6 space-y-3 text-gray-700">
          <p>• Expanded degrees of freedom in force sensing</p>
          <p>• Higher-resolution interaction modeling</p>
          <p>• Improved fidelity of contact dynamics measurement</p>
        </div>

      </div>

    </div>

    <div class="mt-12">
      <a href="/technology" class="text-black font-medium underline">
        Explore full technical architecture →
      </a>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

  <!-- =========================
  APPLICATIONS
  ========================== -->

  <section class="py-24">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">

    <h2 class="text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-gray-500">
      Applications
    </h2>

    <p class="mt-4 text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 max-w-3xl">
      Systems that require precise understanding of physical interaction.
    </p>

    <p class="mt-6 text-lg text-gray-600 leading-8 max-w-4xl">
      High-resolution sensing of force, pressure, and shear enables improved performance in systems where physical interaction is central to function, reliability, or safety. Tactonic Technologies’ sensing platforms are designed to operate across a wide range of such environments.
    </p>

    <div class="mt-16 grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">

      <div class="border border-gray-200 rounded-2xl p-6">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900">
          Industrial Systems
        </h3>
        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600 leading-7">
          Environments where reliable physical interaction with variable components
          is required under changing conditions.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="border border-gray-200 rounded-2xl p-6">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900">
          Automated Logistics
        </h3>
        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600 leading-7">
          Systems involving the handling, sorting, and manipulation of heterogeneous
          objects with uncertain geometry and material properties.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="border border-gray-200 rounded-2xl p-6">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900">
          Agricultural Systems
        </h3>
        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600 leading-7">
          Environments involving delicate, deformable, or irregular organic materials
          requiring adaptive physical interaction.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="border border-gray-200 rounded-2xl p-6">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900">
          Research & Robotics Platforms
        </h3>
        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600 leading-7">
          Experimental systems exploring advanced manipulation, sensing, and embodied
          interaction in controlled or exploratory environments.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="border border-gray-200 rounded-2xl p-6">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900">
          Defense & Field Systems
        </h3>
        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600 leading-7">
          Robust systems operating in unstructured, unpredictable environments where
          physical interaction reliability is critical.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>

  </div>
</section>

  <!-- =========================
  PARTNERSHIPS CTA
  ========================== -->

  <section class="bg-gray-900 text-white py-24">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">

    <div class="max-w-3xl">

      <h2 class="text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-gray-400">
        Collaboration
      </h2>

      <p class="mt-4 text-4xl font-bold leading-tight">
        Advancing physical interaction sensing through research and system-level collaboration.
      </p>

      <p class="mt-8 text-lg text-gray-300 leading-8">
        Tactonic Technologies works with research institutions, industry partners, and public-sector programs to explore and advance sensing systems for real-time physical interaction understanding.
      </p>

      <p class="mt-6 text-lg text-gray-300 leading-8">
        We are particularly interested in collaborations involving advanced robotics, experimental sensing architectures, and systems requiring high-resolution measurement of force, pressure, and shear dynamics.
      </p>

      <div class="mt-10 flex gap-4">
        <a href="/contact" class="bg-white text-black px-6 py-3 rounded-lg">
          Contact
        </a>

        <a href="/technology" class="border border-gray-600 px-6 py-3 rounded-lg">
          Technology Overview
        </a>
      </div>

    </div>

  </div>
</section>

</MainLayout>